OL,3,CAlleged Myleene Klass stalker sent
OL,4,CNicola Sturgeon letter 'signed in
OL,5,Cblood'
OL,7,FAn alleged stalker accused of causing
OL,8,Fserious alarm to Myleene Klass sent a
OL,9,Fletter to Nicola Sturgeon, he said was
OL,10,F"signed in blood" and which "pledged
OL,11,Fhis soul to Satan".
OL,13,F61-year-old Peter Windsor from
OL,14,FBirmingham was arrested in January
OL,15,F2023 over the letter, which was posted
OL,16,Fto the former first minister in 2020,
OL,17,Fbut a decision was taken not to
OL,18,Fprosecute him, a trial at Birmingham
OL,19,FCrown Court was told.
