OL,4,CNicola Sturgeon letter 'signed in
OL,5,Cblood'
OL,7,FProsecutors allege Windsor, who
OL,8,Fsuffers from schizophrenia, stalked
OL,9,Fboth Ms Klass and her Classic FM
OL,10,Fcolleague Katie Breathwick by sending
OL,11,Fitems, including an air pistol,
OL,12,Fhandcuffs and details of a DIY will
OL,13,Fkit, to the station's central London
OL,14,Fstudios between 2020 and 2024.
OL,16,FWindsor gave evidence in his defence
OL,17,Fon Thursday (October 2nd) after agreed
OL,18,Ffacts were read to the jury detailing
OL,19,Ftwo letters he sent to Ms Sturgeon in
OL,20,FOctober 2020 and October 2022.
