OL,7,FThe agreed facts, read into the court
OL,8,Frecord by prosecutor Timothy Sapwell,
OL,9,Fsaid of the first letter: "The
OL,10,Fdefendant sent a letter to the first
OL,11,Fminister for Scotland, Nicola Sturgeon.
OL,13,F"It was signed by him. In it he said
OL,14,Fthat he might visit her to discuss
OL,15,Fgroups of people with whom he appeared
OL,16,Fto take issue, including Freemasons,
OL,17,Fpoliticians and doctors.
