OL,7,F"He also said that he pledged his soul
OL,8,Fto Satan and that the letter was
OL,9,Fsigned in blood. There was some dried
OL,10,Fblood on it."
OL,12,FThe second letter to the then first
OL,13,Fminister, which bore Windsor's name
OL,14,Fand address, expressed hostility to
OL,15,Fvarious groups and made reference to
OL,16,Fkilling people, the court heard.
