OL,7,FWindsor was arrested by Police
OL,8,FScotland officers at his home in
OL,9,FJanuary 2023 on suspicion of
OL,10,Fthreatening behaviour as a result of
OL,11,Fthe two letters.
OL,13,FHe was then interviewed at
OL,14,FBirmingham's Perry Barr custody suite
OL,15,Fand released pending further inquiries
OL,16,Fand "ultimately a decision was taken
OL,17,Fnot to prosecute him because he was
OL,18,Fnot resident in Scotland".
