OL,7,FGiving evidence to the jury from the
OL,8,Fwitness box, Windsor said the letter
OL,9,Fsent to Ms Sturgeon was "just a joke"
OL,10,Fand denied that a map of Edinburgh
OL,11,Ffound on the wall of his home showed a
OL,12,Fdesire to visit her.
OL,14,FAsked about the first letter saying he
OL,15,Fwanted to visit Ms Sturgeon, Windsor
OL,16,Fanswered: "That wasn't serious. I
OL,17,Fwanted to visit the Royal Yacht
OL,18,FBritannia.
