OL,7,F"I just thought I would write a black
OL,8,Fcomedy-type note ` just a script in an
OL,9,Facting thing."
OL,11,FWindsor, who has used multiple names
OL,12,Fincluding Peter Szymanski and changed
OL,13,Fhis surname to Windsor by deed poll,
OL,14,Fappeared in the witness box wearing a
OL,15,Flight grey sweatshirt and dark grey
OL,16,Fjogging bottoms.
