OL,7,FAnswering questions from defence
OL,8,Fbarrister Philip Brunt, Windsor, who
OL,9,Fhas no previous convictions, said he
OL,10,Fhad sent the items to the radio
OL,11,Fpresenters and Ms Sturgeon as a
OL,12,F"pretend weird" acting performance.
OL,14,FSome of the items posted to Mrs
OL,15,FBreathwick, including a stamp
OL,16,Fcollection, had been an attempt to put
OL,17,Fher mind at rest that he was not a
OL,18,F"weirdo criminal" drug addict, Windsor
OL,19,Fsaid.
