OL,7,FSaying he had a "pretend obsession"
OL,8,Fwith Mrs Breathwick and Ms Klass and
OL,9,Fwanted to get in the newspapers,
OL,10,FWindsor added: "I thought I would be
OL,11,Farrested and let go the same day."
OL,13,FFormer Hear'Say star Ms Klass told the
OL,14,Fjury on Wednesday how she felt "sheer
OL,15,Fterror" after being sent a gun, a
OL,16,Fsilver ring and a police uniform.
