OL,7,FMrs Breathwick told the court on
OL,8,FTuesday of her horror at receiving a
OL,9,Fletter with details of a DIY will-
OL,10,Fwriting kit and other "raving" and
OL,11,F"unhinged" mail from Windsor, who she
OL,12,Fsaid left her in fear of her safety.
OL,14,FAsked what his motivation had been for
OL,15,Fsending the items to the presenters,
OL,16,FWindsor responded: "Just to try and
OL,17,Fdraw attention to the plight of people
OL,18,Fwho have been on benefit, like I have,
OL,19,Ffor 30 years.
