OL,7,F"They are always criminal suspects and
OL,8,Fpolice always come around to them for
OL,9,Fdoing the slightest thing.
OL,11,F"I thought I will be a bit
OL,12,Fcontroversial. And maybe more people
OL,13,Fwill know me and say 'there he is' in
OL,14,Fthe pub."
OL,16,FWindsor denies two counts of stalking,
OL,17,Fcausing serious alarm or distress.
OL,19,FThe trial at Birmingham Crown Court
OL,20,Fcontinues.
